comments: Walker (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Harris' (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact.
Theis (BOS) slightly turns as he establishes a picking position in Simmons' (PHI) path but does not deliver any contact.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Simmons' (PHI) path.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal defensive position alongside Walker (BOS) and absorbs the body contact initiated by Walker during his driving shot attempt.
Green (BOS) places an arm on Theis' (BOS) front but does not extend or deliver contact during Theis' play at the basket.
Green (BOS) makes marginal contact with Milton's (PHI) lower body at the start of the drive.
Smart (BOS) makes contact with Milton's (PHI) body during his driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) momentarily places two hands on Simmons' (PHI) backside but does not extend or deliver contact during the pick.
Green (PHI) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes contact with the ball during the steal, any follow-through contact to Theis' (BOS) arm is marginal.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Smart's (BOS) path.
Theis (BOS) slightly extends a hand to Embiid's (PHI) backside at the beginning of the pick. The contact is marginal and does not prevent Embiid from establishing picking position.
Theis (BOS) is drawn into the air and makes contact with Harris' (PHI) body prior to the pass.
Thybulle (PHI) makes contact with Walker's (BOS) arm at the end of the drive.
Smart (BOS) continues moving into Thybulle's (PHI) space and dislodges him from his defensive position off ball.
Walker (BOS) makes marginal contact with Simmons (PHI) with his off-arm during his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) makes marginal contact with Green (PHI) as they simultaneously grab the rebound. A jump ball is correctly assessed following this play.
After the release of the pass, Smart (BOS) takes a step towards Thybulle (PHI) as he is airborne and creates the marginal contact as Thybulle returns to the floor.
Walker (BOS) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Harris (PHI) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Theis' (BOS) body as he taps the rebound away from Theis.
